<BLOCK1><TI><UNDER>JUDGMENT</UNDER></TI>
<P>In accordance with the attached Reasons for Judgment:</P>
<P>The appeal from reassessments made pursuant to the <EM>Income Tax Act</EM> with respect to the Appellant's 2012 and 2013 taxation years is allowed, without costs, and the reassessments are referred back to the Minister of National Revenue for reconsideration and reassessment in accordance with the attached Reasons for Judgment.</P>
