<P1>6. The Minister reassessed the Appellant nil tax, interest, and penalties for the taxation year ended October 31, 2013 by a Notice of Reassessment dated March 16, 2016.</P1>
<P1>7. The Appellant objected to the reassessments for the taxation years ended October 31, 2010, October 31, 2011 and October 31, 2012, and purported to object to the nil reassessment for the taxation year ended October 31, 2013 by Notice of Object ion May 17, 2016.</P1>
<P1>8. In respect to the purported objection for the taxation year ended October 31, 2013, the Minister advised the Appellant that no appeal can be instituted from notification that not tax is payable through a letter dated June 14, 2016.</P1>
